LI %uc774 %ub9dd%ud560 %uc73d%ubd84%uc528 %ubb34%uc2a8 %uc77c%uc774%uc5ec%uc694? %uc2f8%uc6b0%ub294%uc18c%ub9ac%uac00 %ub4e4%ub9ac%ub10c%ub370 -%uc5ed%uc2dc (%uc6a9%uc774%uc168%uad70. %uc544%uae4c%ub294%uc800%uac00 %uc2e4%ub824%ud588%uc2b5%ub2c8%ub2e4 ALL %uc774%ub807%uac8c %ud325%uc9c0%uae30 %uc0ac%ub098%uc6b4%uc874%uc81c%ub294 .%uc800%uc628 %ub9cc%ub098%uc11c. %uc815%ud655%uc6a9 %ubc1b%uc744 %ub358%uc9c0%ub7ec%uace0 %ud588%uc5b4%uc694. %uacf5%uaca9%ud558%ub824%ub358 %uac83%uc740 -o%ub2d8%ub2c8%ub2e4. %uc544%ub2c8%uc624, %uae30%uc6b4%uc5d0%uc608%ubbfc%ud558%uba74 %uadf8%ub9b4 %uc218%ub3c4 %uc788%uc9c0. %ube44%uc2b7%ud55c %ubd80%ub958%ub97c %ub9ce%uc774 %ub9cc%ub098%uc11c, %uc548%ub098%uc624. %uc2a4%ub975 ,%ub0b4 %ubc18%ub9ac%uac00 %uc2ec%ud788 %ud06c%uac8c %ubc18%uc751%ud558%uc5ec , %uc774%ucabd%uc774 %ubbf8%uc548%ud55c%uac70%ub9de%uc9c0%uc694. %uac00%uac8c%ub97c %ubd80%uc21c %uac74 %ub0b4 %ubaa8%ub450 %ubcc0%uc0c1%ud5c8 %uc8fc%ub9ac%ub2e4. %ub2e4%ub9cc %uc800%ucabd %ubd84%uc5d0%uac8c%ub3c4 %uc798 %uc124%uba85%ud574%uc8fc%uac00%ub97c %ubd80%ud0c1%ud558%uc624. ???? %uc637%uac00%uc9c0%uace0%uc640%uc918%uc2dc %uace0%ub9d9%ub2e4%uc6a9%uc544. 24%uc2dc %uc21c%ubcfc%uac00%uc774 %uc774%uac8c ilolo %uc774%ub7f0%uc11c%ub7f0 %uc77c%ubbf8 %uc788%uc5c8%uc9c0~! %uadf8%ub7ec%uace0%ubcf4%ub2c8, %uc694%uba70%uce60%uc740 %ub0a8%ud3b8%uc774%ub791%ub178%ub290%ub77c %uc5ec%uae30%uc628%ubaa9%uc801%uc744 %uc78a%uc5c8%uc5c8%ub124. %uce74%uc77c%ub3c4 %uc815%uae30%ub97c %ub108%ubb34 %ub9ce%uc774 %uc783%uc5b4%uc11c %ud798%ub4e4%uc5b4%ud558%uace0, %ub2e4%uc2dc %uc9d1%uc73c%ub85c %ub3cc%ub824%ubcf4%ub0b4%uc544 %uaca0%uc5b4. %uc544%uae4c%ub0b4%uac00 %ud55c %ub9d0 %ud328%ubb38%uc774%uba74%u30fb %ub3d9, %uc790%uc758%uc2dd%uc774 %ub108%ubb34 %uac10%ud558%uad6c%ub098 %ub0b4 %ubc18%ub824%ub97c %uc774%ub534 %ud0c1%ud55c %uacf5%uae30%uc18d%uc5d0 %ub450%uae30 %uc2eb%uc5b4%uc11c %uadf8%ub7ec%ub290%ub2c8%ub77c %ubab9%uc4f8 %uc228%uc26c%ub294 %uac83 %uc880 %ubcf4%ub77c %uadc0%uc5fd%uace0%uc548%uc4f0%uaecd%uc9c0 %uc54a%uc73c%ub098? %uba3c%uc9c0, %uc778%uac04 %ub188%ub4e4 %uc548%ub155%ud558%uc2dc%uc694. %uc544%ubc84%uc9c0 %ub370%ub9ac%ub9ac , %ubd24%uc2b5%ub2c8%ub2e4 %ubbc0%uc2dc%uace0 %uac00%ub3c4 %ub420%uae4c%uc694? %uc544. %uc774%uc800 %uac00%uc2e0%ub2e4%uace0 %ud558%ub2c8 %uc124%uc12c%ud574%uc11c %uc800%ub3c4 %ubaa8%ub974%uae30 %ub450%uc2dc%uac04%uc774%ub098 %u096b2 %ub3cc%ub9c8%uac00%uc11c %uc798%uc9c0%ub0b4%uc2dc%uace0, %uacbd%uae30 %uaf2d %ucc59%uae30%uc2dc%uace0, %uc0dd%uac01%ub098%uba74 %uac00%uace1 %ub180%ub7ec%uc624%uc2dc%uace0%uc694. %ud56d%uc0c1 %uc81c%uac00 %ucf58%uc131%ud558%uace0 %uc788%ub2e4%ub294 %uac70 / %ube14%ub9ac%ube14%ub9ac %uc77c%uc9c0 %ubbf8%uc2dc%uace0 %uc5bc%uac04%uc6d4%ub77c %uc544%ud2b8%ub2cc %uac00%uc2e4 %ub5a0, %uacf5%uc8fc%ub2d8%uc740 %uc800%ub791 %uc74c%uc528%uac00 -%uc798%uc815%uaca8 %ub4dc%ub9b4%ud14c%ub2c8 -%uac71%uce60 %ub9c8%uc2dc%uace0.. %uadf8%ub798, %uc54c%uaca0%ub124 %ub2ed%uc694%ub9ac %uc798 %uba39%uace0%uac00%ub124 %uc8fc%uc778%uc7a5! SF %ubcf4%uc138! %uadf8 %ud638%uce6d%uc73c%ub85c %ub9cc%uc871 %ud558%ub294%uad6c%ub098 %ucd5c%uc6b0%ud601! %uc911 305%ud638%ub97c %ub5a0%ub098%ub294%uc2a8%uac04%uae4c%uc9c0 %ucc29%uc6b0%ud601 %uc9c0%uac04%uc2ed%uc0ac%uc7a5%uc73c%ub85c %uc54c%uace0 %uc788%ub294%uce74%uc77c%uc774%uc5c8%ub2e4.
